General.Name: Fintech Ecosystem Development Corp Unit
General.Description: Fintech Ecosystem Development Corp. does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to acquire companies in the financial technology development sector in South Asia. Fintech Ecosystem Development Corp. was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Collegeville, Pennsylvania.
